answers.answer: def not.normal could have preeclampsia please go to er better safe than sorry but your vision.suppose be.normal... not ttryna scare you keep us updated
Changes in vision can be just blood pressure changes but as far along as you are it can also be a sign of preterm labor. Probably better safe than sorry and see a doc about it.
Now I'm very worried. Do I go to l & d or the er?

I would go to l & d bc they have more specialized training in pregnancy and won't just brush it off like a busy ER doc might. Plus your wait time to be seen will probably be shorter. They can always send you down to the ER if they think that's better
Okay thank you, I will keep you ladies updated.
